<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It will be nice if i can give a table prefix for Zend_Db_Table().</p>

<p>Example:</p>

<p>Zend_Db_Table::setDefaultAdapter('mysqli');
Zend_Db_Table::setTablePrefix('myprefix_');</p>

<p>class MyTable extends Zend_Db_Table
{
$_name = 'mytablename';
}</p>

<p>$table = new MyTable();
output from $table-&gt;info():
array('name' =&gt; 'myprefix_mytablename', 'prefix' =&gt; 'myprefix_', ...);</p>

    </div>
